page.title: 11Hedge/Soil Survey,N. Tregony
page.content: {Hedge Survey}is a survey of all the herbacious plants in the hedgerows North of Tregony. Hogweed,Nettle,Goosegrass,Jack by the Hedge,Foxglove,Daisy,Dock,Herb Robert,Red Campion,Bracken,Hedge Parsley,Willow Herb,Cow Parsley, Navelwort,Greater Stichwort,Cat's Ear ,Wood Sage,Sorrel,Chickweed,Dandilion, Germandine Speedwell,Wood Avons,Ground Ivy,Hedge Bedstraw,Bluebell,Wild Garlic,Wild Strawberry,Ribbed Plantain ,Birdsfoot Trefoil,Tufed Vetch. {Soil Samples}were taken from around the river Fal.In parts per million. Grid Ref:463290 Contains:Zinc 58,Cadmium <1,Copper 40,Lead 30. Grid Ref:469934. Contains: Zinc 121,Cadmium 1,Copper 45,Lead 75. Grid Ref: 427960. Contains: Zinc 12, Cadmium <1,Copper 10,Lead 10.
